= Hosted engine VM management enhancements =

{{Feature|name=Hosted engine VM management enhancements |modules=api,engine,hosted-engine-setup,vdsm|status=Design & research|version=3.6}}

== Summary ==

Allow editing the Hosted engine VM, storage domain, disks, networks etc

== Owner ==
<!--This should link to your home wiki page so we know who you are-->

